schools.name: Byron P Steele Ii High School

data.description: This stunning one-story gem boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and offers a seamless blend of elegance and comfort.  Step inside and be amazed by the open floor plan that welcomes you with abundant natural light. The heart of this home is the expansive living area, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment.  Beautiful LVP throughout the living areas, bedrooms and bathrooms! Ceramic tile at the entry and the Kitchen. For allergy suffers, no carpet! Imagine hosting family gatherings, movie nights, or cozy evenings - this home has it all! The Master Suite is truly a retreat within itself, featuring a generous layout and a large walk-in closet that will satisfy even the most enthusiastic shoppers. The attached master bathroom offers both convenience and luxury, making mornings a breeze. Picture yourself unwinding on the covered patio, enjoying the peaceful serenity of your backyard oasis. Whether it's morning coffee or evening sunsets, this space is sure to become your favorite spot to unwind. For those who love to cook and entertain, the large kitchen is a dream come true. With plenty of beautiful granite counter space, large walk-in pantry, and a refrigerator included. Location is key, and this home has it all! The subdivision is conveniently situated just across the street from Steele High School, making school days a breeze. Plus, for our military families, the proximity to Randolph AFB and Fort Sam offers a shortened commute, allowing you to spend more quality time at home. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful, one-story home yours! With its spacious layout, fantastic features, and unbeatable location, it's sure to check all the boxes on your dream home list.
